# {{ plugin_name }}

{{ description }}

A provider plugin for OpenComputer. Providers wrap an LLM API behind
``BaseProvider`` so the agent loop can call any backend uniformly.

## Install

Copy this directory into one of:

- `~/.opencomputer/plugins/{{ plugin_id }}/` (global)
- `~/.opencomputer/profiles/<name>/plugins/{{ plugin_id }}/` (profile-local)

Or run `opencomputer plugin install <path-to-this-dir>`.

